  "unresolvedTextByHash": {
    "ed5cbac7a23570df9900373ca0098ed98c12fed905166b9446bbce1b00ce63d7": "Hi [?]!",
    "82dad1aa37b0acfdf53878a67c19aaef5934ff5ff3f456ea07df25fce4843fcd": "Sure thing! Come on, [?], let's go talk to the scribe",
    "acd9f029e7df0f17ebf52c440cab3d91420167aea9abb6334de9a3efc7ea26bc": "I've got a strange feeling about this mace, [?]. Maybe when we find out about it, it will shed some light onto my destiny. Come on, let's show it to the scribe.",
    "93449d3fbcd32f9406b4ebef9322ab998da176fce65e2860a9f548f3e3dd5972": "Not right now, Oldak. I'm helping [?]!",
    "b121d80bda091d0f5f95b5de5c7043d2f86ef0e2289201424c25ae86b18e5ab9": "[?] helped us to finish the dig! Look what she dug up!",
    "991a7b6ddcec53efba51873b4322d751247b435c5b35edb5e933f8c471665c08": "[?] says that's a kind of weapon.",
    "dfed2251b27052bdc07e73b847e15d34e6185fc1260d4fb873f593498cf1c02c": "Not yet. Come on, [?]! We should go and ask the goblin generals about it!",
    "068d3f50840fd09230b42bac9acf37eab47fde4deda5776f232cddcc59e10367": "Thanks Oldak! Okay, [?], let's go!",
    "cb5a125abad64e0cf238fea6f3acfb504488b451bb748eb3960d24b0fd04f132": "So this is the Goblin Village! It's so different from Dorgesh-Kaan, isn't it, [?]?",
    "dfda42494d6d6dc2adf6bbe7da7f15c971bba51e8ab0b51d462fb748adda746e": "[?], where are you?",
    "8acb6a7aeef2d4a0dc6b173289d9dc3de36ca3b67b527a85d9847b86c4655fc3": "Sorry about that, [?]! Oldak's calculations aren't always exact!",
    "cceb035f732ee0bbb5df4e2430b9e4dcc3c01cdc927d60e0a08546aae98f5cd8": "So this is how goblins on the surface live! Come on, [?], lets talk to them!",
    "324a2d9a55624a8da00cbcd7d479035cf788b169fb696a1d94cef5d45396e487": "I'll meet you back in Dorgesh-Kaan, [?].",
    "2ee97a529f1bcb8a91c77a481f58ed82ada57c9f14d8386a7714f21a525e9c79": "Come on [?], let's get back to the Goblin Village on the surface! Shall we go?",
    "be1e814241e816092511d70002127e5d53fa19474785bd0dbf7ba9b65dd922ec": "What are we doing here, [?]? We should get to the Goblin Village!",
    "e78b9d5427b0c743d089eb11872ade3e0ef09f0e0f9006a8d3ad7367e68203a4": "Help, [?]! What should I say?",
    "a62d5cf977120ff0cc850bc9deb9f37e49200b6bba2fc33f7dd45840ad90bced": "The shots came from the top of that tower, [?]! Can you see anything?",
    "edb251c708019c2f11c0ace0b51579f117cc3e59cada4c3a24839741fcfb57f9": "Quick, [?]! Shoot him while I have him distracted!",
    "9901da107cf12ba008f6d4d49c25986294c50ad25e3d926f20e76ade9a51c4da": "Quick, [?]! Untie me before the train comes!",
    "7735cdd0716fa5346069ade0b704baf6f8cf60981b353d653035d00df18e4e30": "You must be the famous [?]!",
    "649ffc5117e0082179ab767bbf397375aeca34a6404d1ddafb2cde271cb1c9f5": "Hi [?]! Have you got our disguises yet?",
    "015d7b3fcaec7fc7ecbc73d8d6e67014928120d88bd451770a14bec15d0b4870": "I will tell you, [?], but not just yet. Finish showing me around Lumbridge and then I'll tell you.",
    "b9133981b7914895d2969139e2b31b832cc09d73b4e1869f9bd9dfe18c892ba3": "It's so enclosed, it could almost be underground. Let's go outside, [?]! I want to see the sun!",
    "905df8cd12e1866c412baca5553b03e93ee22e2a482e0d061f8dea0c51de6617": "I'm sorry, [?]. I'd like to show you around the city, but the council has decided not to let any surface-dwellers in yet.",
    "723a91a01a20d0aebfc6c1c3fe2313369a3e65708e843f5df5e2073d9c992e3a": "I wish I could show it to you, [?]!",
    "d268200a34feb4d076e30d7b8a09c1601a38f6c936bf8e634f2eef69b3183943": "No thank you! [?] is showing me around!",
    "95df8f0eecccb0c47ffb699d629ba2f3c5f3916fcd90fffa7372af565f16fae3": "Let's go, [?].",
    "5cdddffc898353e88bc0de3a083925f1c949a224a8f909116e27e417719926e5": "Never mind, [?]. I don't think we need to go to Al Kharid anyway!",
    "11152477fb488bee473acb575ede8d5c420ed87239a0098b8a62158eb0005098": "I've hardly SEEN the surface yet! [?] just dragged me back down here!",
    "ed0013492246b7d4c5aed29d669ea4b5f37f8ccad49de858e6d1c7a111d02d04": "There are so many people around! You must introduce me to them, [?]!",
    "e0882eab4b17bc1462cd1e783a392402acc8ad58380b0655aa053de57506e371": "But at least you're friendly, [?]!",
    "db70914753e4723ed78191e77681a35e4602e9f931c118972d6ba698919bbe60": "Are there still goblins living on the surface, [?]? Are there any near Lumbridge?",
    "e41f9c86a4a658f9cf924c078b93cacb4947f830648eff6cc164d3ab13fc595a": "Ever since then I've wondered what the sign meant. But perhaps you will help me to find out, [?]!",
    "813cecc328ff211c7515a9f5549f3fe21ab07adff7f1113b56784068a86f9534": "We're getting a bit far away from Lumbridge, [?]. I'd like to see the rest of the world someday but not right now. Let's stick to Lumbridge for now.",
    "794607cb6033a622376985e804cab8e1f0dae9fe51363e4244620b4102b1568d": "Listen to what that speaker's saying, [?]!",
    "85b81f58623dab05a67496143e3c3017884ab7ec6f721d2b975dcd4af1e58c40": "We can get through this if we work together, [?]. But I can't get too close to the guards or they'll see I'm not human.",
    "3e78509915dfc5f24c3d95499eb32bb77eabc8a2ae7b4ca2f6c76d0918913b04": "It's a special technique with the bone crossbow. If we both get out of this alive I'll teach you, [?]!",
    "b7d482d7118e2c786ff1e7b43bec9bf870ae4710c76c02870163dd878bf1688e": "[?]! Wake up!",
    "1ab001fdcca68e40327ec2f7f9f44bad600e674eb42db62e9caae5a5fac9ff50": "Thanks, [?]!",
    "b19574dee0696add2f2952c26f41b6939858968e962177e95b2aeb1ca464a50c": "We got him, [?]!",
    "d2e7a78e7359216c1a015a4fbe408b87c0e3222b379a8e8079c24eab3f212554": "We've got to do something, [?]! They're going to--",
    "9c9bfc27e862e2f226966d489be3fdc7644c5a4b80424ec678ccf17f26481427": "What are you doing? Noo! Don't kill me! [?], help me!",
    "2e1bc041d28c7f9658db9358b9fcdab892295d789797484d79adbfcaf96f28e5": "They killed me, didn't they, [?]?",
    "ebb95a4d9504624753565b093f5f90c63ebf646761461a0db82b22c81e6db1ec": "The plot! [?], I've got to tell you what I heard outside the meeting room!",
    "35adc7da7c89aa04b242ba9899d9fadfaca5a0ec3fba0df0da6a516272718389": "Let's go, [?]! We've got to get to the Lumbridge water mill so we can foil Sigmund's plan!",
    "91d4dc34e13e84ef4352da4077d607d39b764bec1e6c371613acd96b64d2eec6": "Do it quickly, [?]! We've got to stop Sigmund from destroying my city!",
    "69efe162cc4b01b6d77ae062c5d9be17d374dae1090024c274bb3abf7c51c518": "It was horrible, [?]!",
    "7ff48b288753bd97867b8efe9d1d2a1ffd303a94bdedb303f04d88a9a04d3ae2": "Let's get them, [?]! I need to save my city and I want to get my revenge!",
    "d5783859f0a7747bcb489d9651367b2d3101b0365a5e23be964c701026170f11": "Quick, [?]! Let's get to the water mill and stop Sigmund from destroying my home!",
    "3a49204fc1096593424b7e574d82e510639869f149ec77d09a6aacf7f4f31ffd": "We've not got time to talk now, Kazgar! [?], you've got to take me to the Lumbridge water mill at once!",
    "f8950e7e5e80b8fa5f1e15a46f406b7f2e0b9495a2a80e11da5c283943e1c703": "Don't you dare go down there without me, [?]! Find some way to get us both down there so I can face Sigmund myself!",
    "a13ce5a79e0105b79b7ebabdbdc2ad2c44b2c88d5bec4c7b7a72e67689e2e01f": "Are you thinking what I'm thinking, [?]?",
    "20688ba6c16f4a839ea888337a03f0c079e45abd32e6cc1d484f92850ac73104": "We've got to stop him, [?]!",
    "54e79dcc87afdbccd0f6cd0c73fedde5b3a9dfff127d546f4a9f225fc474b6c0": "Let's get them, [?]!",
    "4b6c64136fcb84f5858831f324f0994d167cc70f1dbade3af11438d6a8acdd10": "Don't leave me, [?]! I can't defeat Sigmund without you!",
    "6e662ee82f402f8bc21ec49176a11841809db9c100789606afa8ecc428b413bf": "Hurry, [?]!",
    "8e56bcf05466f4bab24466f4190c23754ab071d6c497aac9cfdbc35caadb365f": "[?]! Thank goodness you're all right! Now let's finish off Sigmund and his cronies before they flood the city!",
    "c6d200f054f0d9ae179b4d827aeb5be51dac0fc1de004d69d8dd558834232b43": "Quick, [?], let's smash that drilling machine before Sigmund returns! Then we can return to Dorgesh- Kaan for a hero's welcome!",
    "5168068dd7edc0ffbdf251cf73fbc9ed9e6bb295db91fc91f04b07b35e3da7ec": "There's no need to go that way, [?]! We can go south along the tunnel to the Dorgeshuun mine.",
    "1b49e2cf67e06098281be26e98f6aecd764dc4083527a968c0694623923f6bd4": "We did it, [?]! My city is safe! Now we can follow that tunnel south back to the mines!",
    "14250eb9e5d21dde884aaf02ddd832194be9a872b6d88ab511275b1752c09f13": "And not all surface-dwellers are bad. Without [?] the city would have been destroyed for sure!",
    "cdc7165279a8f42653a13dac875882d7ba529b94302980abb55e8dc16d254f94": "Thank you for taking me on that adventure, [?]! I'll show you how to use the bone crossbow like I promised I would!",
    "b0c8113f135386786796c4dd00e62acd61a8b12e6f09d23c40e3df295b5f774f": "Come find me in the city if you ever want to chat, [?]. I'm going to go and think about what Juna said about my destiny. I don't know what it will involve, but I have a feeling we will adventure together again!",
    "c71f2b3e9647db0c732ca170dd1ae6f9635a0d05f2b4e920ab6a9cddbb8df4ac": "Hello, [?]!",
    "050b1a41199b625f1d42affab691e8339e9af56f8621a4f3d3ccebc644f4dede": "What do you think, [?]?",
    "4db246a61b00ea7a893a58f61d76ad7b6097b6fa4bb47643beb716d001fe6ebe": "[?] is a friend. You can tell him.",
    "d1d9b8175f8543ba169e81d5a0af460f036bbe8b0e2b146d72f35cc5cbc97bfa": "[?] is a friend. You can tell her.",
    "e90c90e7d071a7fd8f8c4c9d87a53eedc3e99eb9e5ff97e11d95c9faa1924025": "[?] is a friend. You can tell them.",
    "0df4552914d549ac83d8dc58cd28716b0b61315f9d29f20c63062e2210b35c6f": "I'll wait until you are, [?].",
    "8d316a0914ead2152c5f7f7c53ac5ca0bf61c838d48d251d0f7e57b515546235": "The entrance to the secret temple must be around here somewhere, [?].",
    "b99989460ad92866c98366dc2d15919eac2cc99a645d42a239e0253882ef583c": "Okay, [?]. I'll meet you back at the cave entrance.",
    "f159483bbc2504a605fd70ec4738bfae599c3fea39c72a93fc49ea535c4d4164": "Thank you, [?]! I'm sorry to leave you, but it looks like you'll have to find out about Yu'biusk on your own. Hopefully you have better luck with that high priest than I did.",
    "e13dd4df98d8933543e64abde3cc9574c6bb904a4c34b4e92f7b6f3f04dd7adf": "Is that you, [?]? Do you have that moving-over-distance sphere?",
    "2a0c8e26264e5d15231034ed190773d7c2f1170a4b851a0104339e823fbafb48": "Could this be it, [?]? Could this be my destiny? Could this be why I was marked by the Tears of Guthix?",
    "4b145cea36a30f28d67775dcac786dcdc2fe0f326162c001f7df0d5e8d47c2c2": "Hey, [?]. This is incredible! I can't believe we're really going to go to Yu'biusk, the Land of the Goblins!",
    "79bf61f6c907b049e24ea995e31343f141bc0fd583fff4d7c49660e548a1e431": "I thought this might be it, [?]. I really did. I thought this place might finally give me some answers, but it's just another dead end.",
    "9b23ecf1fe130cc8bab9009a2d30858fa25f53792864124cee35d62431932ca6": "What's happening? [?]!",
    "2ecc341e254c087dcfde92184c7e8e56f5f7820ef2a0bd17d17144eea5415326": "You should keep it safe, [?]!",
    "ef923612c0e46bd09e251dbc4c8412bdd94fef270b35d74b7041d8fbf80a93db": "I thought you had the ancient goblin mace, [?]. But I found it in the caves.",
    "fab2960ac63e356c7620c8067f11771a3bb8461ee61ad448bb6c35eac84fc35a": "Don't worry, I'm sure [?] will help keep us safe from the H.A.M. people!",
    "8cb074f0b7027aa0ee6e58f35475972cbbd740bef640f051f9370bda237447be": "Oh, hello, [?]!",
    "b1447d539cd4a005ce3bf2859f052f954a1aee6e08a112a7866d8203ebad096c": "Maybe someday we'll find out! Oh, hello, [?]!",
    "c5e6ed184cebda3bfdd873e4371063af528eb5a103a6eaa9654e761fdf47cea1": "Alright. Hello, [?]."
  }
}